==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unhair
<hw>Un*hair"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>hair</ets>.]</ety> <def>To deprive of hair, or of
hairs; <as>as, to <ex>unhair</ex> hides for leather</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I 'll <qex>unhair</qex> thy head.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unhallow</ent>⟦br⟧
